title: More on us
line1: We have been treating complementary medicine for over 12 years and have helped rehabilitate a lot of people.
line2: Oxygen is essential for our survival, but unfortunately we do not get enough oxygen for the blood in the normal living environment.
line3: Pressure cell therapy allows for the supply of 100% pure medical oxygen at high pressure, so that more oxygen helps nourish the cells and tissues - a significant process in improving health
